Q. What is Duke Jia?

Duke Jia is a globally recognized brand of computerized embroidery, quilting, and
perforation machines, designed for precision, speed, and industrial reliability. It represents
innovation in textile automation, combining advanced technology with durable engineering.
Q. Who owns the Duke Jia brand?

Duke Jia is owned and marketed by Hari Chand Anand & Co. (HCA) - a pioneer in
garment and textile machinery in India.
Q. What is the history of the Duke Jia brand?

The Duke Jia brand was developed under HCA Group, building on over five decades of
experience in textile and industrial automation. It was created to provide world-class
embroidery and quilting technology tailored for Indian and global markets.
The brand is known for its durability, precision, and advanced servo-controlled systems,
offering complete automation solutions for embroidery, quilting, and perforation.
